Northampton have ruled out winger George North for the game against Clermont Auvergne on Saturday . 
  The 22-year-old was knocked unconscious against Wasps on Friday night . 
  North has been sent to see a neurosurgeon following his third head injury in two months . 
  North was struck by Nathan Hughes's knee as he scored a try . 
  The Saints have ruled him out of their game against the French side . 
 